metadata.name: PURRcast Genesis
metadata.description: This beautiful POAP, made by the one and only Bananakin, represents a moment in time when Purrnelope's Country Club came together with CyberKongz to breed the CyberKongz in the KittyBank. Eclectic Method serenaded us with his sick beats, while Carlini8 took the CyberKongz to a private area "to do their thing". The Legend that is Coco_Bear donated 500 $BANANA that fell from the MetaSky into our wallets! Leading up to the event, ImporterExporter made the sickest graphics, really showcasing the creativity in this space.
